10,000 products are reportedly made from trees. Through chemistry, the humble woodpile is yielding chemicals, plastics and fabrics that were beyond comprehension when an axe first felled a Texas tree.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-fill\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">了解更多</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:2:\"id\";i:10331;s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:38:\"Media and text with image on the right\";}s:7:\"content\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:762:\"\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center is-style-default\" style=\"grid-template-columns:auto 56%\"><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Shore with Blue Sea</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color wp-block-paragraph\" style=\"color:#636363;font-size:17px;line-height:1.1\">Eleanor Harris&nbsp;(American, 1901-1942)</p>\n</div><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/art-02.jpg\" alt=\"绿色和棕色的乡村景观通向明亮的蓝色海洋和略带多云的天空，以油画颜料完成。\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:4:\"meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:13:\"wpop_keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"wpop_description\";s:66:\"Media and text block with image to the right and text to the left.\";s:19:\"wpop_viewport_width\";i:1200;s:16:\"wpop_block_types\";a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}s:11:\"wpop_locale\";s:5:\"zh_CN\";s:15:\"wpop_wp_version\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"wpop_contains_block_types\";s:43:\"core/heading,core/media-text,core/paragraph\";s:9:\"footnotes\";s:0:\"\";}s:14:\"category_slugs\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\