ument notes for future orders</td><td>Reusable project record</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Follow-up File Structure</h2>\n<p>For ongoing cooperation, we can organize each project around a simple file structure:</p>\n<ul><li>Product name and application scenario</li><li>Drawing version and sample photos</li><li>Material, hardness or density, thickness, adhesive, and process notes</li><li>Supplier quote parameters, MOQ, tooling, and lead time</li><li>Certificate/document status: RoHS, REACH, UL94, TDS, SDS, ISO 9001 if available</li><li>Sample feedback, packaging notes, and repeat order reference</li></ul>\n<h2>How This Helps Long-term Cooperation</h2>\n<p>Many gasket projects are not one-time decisions. A buyer may start with one enclosure gasket, then add cabinet strips, foam pads, adhesive-backed parts, or another application. A reusable project record helps reduce repeated explanation, speeds up new quotations, and keeps material and document history clearer.</p>','Service &amp; Follow-up','','inherit','closed','closed','','103-revision-v1','','','2026-07-10 02:03:24','2026-07-09 18:03:24','',103,'http://localhost:8080/?p=114',0,'revision','',0),(123,1,'2026-07-10 03:01:21','2026-07-09 19:01:21','<div class=\"intro-band\"><p>Industry notes, product selection guides, compliance explanations, and sourcing articles for enclosure gasket buyers.</p></div>','Insights','','publish','closed','closed','','insights','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/insights/',0,'page','',0),(133,0,'2026-07-10 03:02:34','2026-07-09 19:02:34','<div class=\"intro-band\"><p>Industry notes, product selection guides, compliance explanations, and sourcing articles for enclosure gasket buyers.</p></div>','Insights','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-10 03:02:34','2026-07-09 19:02:34','',123,'http://localhost:8080/?p=133',0,'revision','',0),(134,0,'2026-07-10 03:02:34','2026-07-09 19:02:34','<p>A technical data sheet is