albridge/assets/trust/factory-screening.png\" alt=\"Factory screening and sample review template\"><figcaption>Screening reference: product fit, process route, sample response, and document support are reviewed together.</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/sealbridge/assets/trust/workshop-glimpse.png\" alt=\"Clean gasket workshop display illustration\"><figcaption>Workshop reference: real supplier names, customer files, and restricted factory photos are shared only when permitted during project communication.</figcaption></figure></div>\n<h2>Certificate and Document Review</h2>\n<p>Certificate support depends on selected material, supplier source, order quantity, and customer requirement. We do not publish customer-specific reports or supplier files publicly by default. Instead, we use a review checklist during project communication.</p>\n<figure class=\"content-figure\"><img src=\"/wp-content/themes/sealbridge/assets/trust/certificate-review.png\" alt=\"Certificate review template illustration\"><figcaption>Illustrative certificate review template. It explains the checking method and is not a public claim that every product has every certificate.</figcaption></figure>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Document Type</th><th>What We Check</th><th>Important Note</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>RoHS</td><td>Material name, test item, test date, supplier or material source</td><td>RoHS is material-related and should match the quoted material.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>REACH</td><td>Declaration or test scope, SVHC reference, document date</td><td>Customer requirement should be confirmed because REACH scope may change.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>UL94</td><td>Material grade, thickness condition, supplier statement or data sheet</td><td>UL94 grade belongs to tested material conditions, not automatically every finished gasket.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>TDS</td><td>Hardness, density, tensile strength, temperature range, compression set</td><td>TDS is useful for engineering review and material comparison.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>SDS</td><td>Material safety handling information and supplier source</td><td>SDS supports safety and handling review, not sealing performance.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>ISO 9001</td><td>Factory quality management certificate if available</td><td>Check company name, validity, certification body, and business scope.</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>What We Do Not Overclaim</h2>\n<p>We do not describe every supplier as certified for every product. We do not claim that a gasket alone has IP65 or IP66 certification. IP-rated sealing belongs to the final enclosure assembly and test condition. Formal document files should be confirmed against the selected material, supplier source, and purchase requirement.</p>','Factory Screening','','inherit','closed','closed','','306-revision-v1','','','2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','',306,'http://localhost:8080/?p=316',0,'revision','',0),(317,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>Electrical enclosure gasket selection should start from the box structure, cover compression, outdoor exposure, material aging, adhesive requirement, and document needs. EPDM foam and silicone gasket materials are common options for outdoor enclosure sealing support.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','How to Choose Electrical Enclosure Gaskets for Outdoor Boxes','Electrical enclosure gas&hellip;','publish','open','open','','choose-electrical-enclosure-gaskets-outdoor-boxes','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/choose-electrical-enclosure-gaskets-outdoor-boxes/',0,'post','',0),(318,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>Control cabinet door seal projects usually need a profile drawing or sample, door gap, material, hardness, color, roll length, and corner joining requirement. These details help avoid quoting the wrong cabinet sealing strip profile.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','Control Cabinet Door Seal Profiles: What Buyers Should Confirm','Control cabinet door sea&hellip;','publish','open','open','','control-cabinet-door-seal-profiles','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/control-cabinet-door-seal-profiles/',0,'post','',0),(319,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>EPDM foam gasket with adhesive is useful for outdoor panels, access covers, and enclosure doors. Buyers should confirm thickness, density, compression gap, adhesive grade, liner type, surface condition, and working environment.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','EPDM Foam Gasket with Adhesive: Key Quote Parameters','EPDM foam gasket with ad&hellip;','publish','open','open','','epdm-foam-gasket-with-adhesive-quote-parameters','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/epdm-foam-gasket-with-adhesive-quote-parameters/',0,'post','',0),(320,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>Silicone gaskets are useful for LED lighting housings, outdoor electronics, and covers exposed to heat, UV, or wider temperature ranges. Solid silicone and silicone foam should be compared based on compression and assembly design.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','Silicone Gaskets for LED Lighting Housings and Outdoor Electronics','Silicone gaskets are use&hellip;','publish','open','open','','silicone-gaskets-led-lighting-outdoor-electronics','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/silicone-gaskets-led-lighting-outdoor-electronics/',0,'post','',0),(321,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>Adhesive backed die cut gaskets help speed up assembly for junction boxes, electronic housings, enclosure covers, and panels. Material, adhesive, release liner, tolerance, and packing format should be confirmed before sampling.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','Adhesive Backed Die Cut Gaskets for Fast Enclosure Assembly','Adhesive backed die cut &hellip;','publish','open','open','','adhesive-backed-die-cut-gaskets-fast-enclosure-assembly','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/adhesive-backed-die-cut-gaskets-fast-enclosure-assembly/',0,'post','',0),(322,1,'2026-07-10 07:27:58','2026-07-09 23:27:58','<p>Custom rubber gaskets according to drawing require material, hardness, dimensions, tolerance, application environment, tooling condition, sample requirement, quantity, and inspection criteria before a useful quotation can be prepared.</p><h2>Buyer Takeaway</h2><p>Confirm the actual application, material data, assembly method, and document requirements before locking the specification.</p>','Custom Rubber Gaskets According to Drawing: From Sample to Quote','Custom rubber gaskets ac&hellip;','publish','open','open','','custom-rubber-gaskets-according-to-drawing-sample-quote','','','2026-07-11 01:07:35','2026-07-10 17:07:35','',0,'http://localhost:8080/custom-rubber-gaskets-according-to-drawing-sample-quote/',0,'post','',0),(332,0,'2026-07-11 01:04:35','2026-07-10 17:04:35','<div class=\"intro-band\"><p>Send the drawing, material, size, quantity, application, and certificate requirements. Clear project details help reduce back-and-forth and improve quotation accuracy.</p></div>\n<h2>Quote Information Checklist</h2>\n<ul class=\"feature-list\"><li>Drawing or photo</li><li>Material target</li><li>Thickness or profile size</li><li>Hardness or density</li><li>Adhesiv